{"id": 1656, "genre": 1001, "title": "你觉得对你来说，怎样才算是“长大”？", "description": "爸妈可能觉得没结婚的都是小孩子，你却觉得自己已经是个中年人了。", "record_count": 4930, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201705031553399opqJDT0ENsdUijK.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-05-03T03:00:55Z", "options": [{"id": 199936, "content": "能够在精神和物质上都独立自主地好好生活", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 940627}, {"id": 200192, "content": "懂得如何去爱人", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 944500}, {"id": 200448, "content": "做事有自己的见解和看法，有可以约束自己行为的力量", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1022726}, {"id": 200960, "content": "能独处 有责任感 有包容心 能承受生活压力 精神压力 可以照顾好自己 可以去爱一个自己所爱的人 拥有一颗感恩的心", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1020118}, {"id": 201216, "content": "能够遇事不惊；崇荣解决问题！凡事不要依靠别人；经济独立，生活独立！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1024725}, {"id": 199681, "content": "经济独立", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 824140}, {"id": 199937, "content": "想贝兼的➕V信 2227887341，曰结", "image": "img/option/option/20170503195436PtLeaAhpnWuN0gEZ.jpg", "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1022018}, {"id": 200193, "content": "看到喜欢的人却说不出来了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1018860}, {"id": 200449, "content": "不再以自我为中心，学会忍让，懂得感恩", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1004783}, {"id": 199938, "content": "懂得什么是责任", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 699912}, {"id": 201474, "content": "老子永远十八岁", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1025632}, {"id": 199683, "content": "责任", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 938946}, {"id": 200195, "content": "正式的像父母出櫃吧。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 627804}, {"id": 200196, "content": "为自己的选择负责，思考未来发展", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1022420}, {"id": 201476, "content": "会爱人，也会爱自己", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1025639}, {"id": 204548, "content": "懂得情绪管理，懂得舍得，懂得自我约束…", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1034126}, {"id": 199941, "content": "独立以及包容", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1022020}, {"id": 200197, "content": "能够自己承担后果，也能分担他们身上的重担", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1022423}, {"id": 201989, "content": "网络时代?只需一部手机?就多一份收入，多一份任性?微信咨询2227887341?每天至少50-300+，上不封顶，半月轻松入2000+?你不比别人差❗️差别就在于你缺少一个有实力的团队和一颗赚钱的心❤️", "image": "img/option/option/20170509080958BiGI2P87YD0bUCmO.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1027056}, {"id": 199942, "content": "懂得什么是责任", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 699912}, {"id": 200710, "content": "一个人生活也觉得充满乐趣", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1007907}, {"id": 201222, "content": "可以独立面对一些事情，并不告诉家人，一个人住，忍住黑夜的寂寞", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1004344}, {"id": 203526, "content": "能够在碰壁或面对刁难你的人时，不受感性的影响，理性应对。现在可以做到独立，但是面对这样的事情，总是会感到委屈，虽然也明白这都是正常的，但是就是控制不住经常泛滥的小情绪", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1029442}, {"id": 199687, "content": "学会思考~不仅仅为自己~", "image": "img/option/option/20170503144325jRilULbxFKz1Z6Jp.jpg", "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 716017}, {"id": 200199, "content": "做事是出于思考而不是冲动", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1022426}, {"id": 204295, "content": "买得起自己想买的东西、承受得住前所未有的压力、还有就是长到一米八?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1013301}, {"id": 200200, "content": "考虑自己的价值，真正的开始依靠自己生活", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1022428}, {"id": 202504, "content": "做事之前多思考，多想想", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 817696}, {"id": 199946, "content": "选择善良\n心情豁达\n人格独立\n经济独立\n氛围快乐", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1020866}, {"id": 200202, "content": "不再纠结什么叫长大", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1019478}, {"id": 201226, "content": "承担责任", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1024756}, {"id": 201482, "content": "保有童心，但不幼稚；寂静中沉淀，但不和装逼者为伍，价值观独立而自信。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 955405}, {"id": 205578, "content": "人格独立，经济独立。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1036183}, {"id": 206858, "content": "孤独的生活", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 908163}, {"id": 199691, "content": "知世故而不世故", "image": null, "praise_count": 44, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1021684}, {"id": 199947, "content": "知道宽容，懂的珍惜", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1022022}, {"id": 228363, "content": "学会爱", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 589122}, {"id": 200204, "content": "财务自由，经济独立，为人处世愈发宽容豁达", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 885464}, {"id": 202764, "content": "在我眼里，我哪有过长大啊，我只想着一直进步，一直怀着颗童心。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1029421}, {"id": 200205, "content": "遇到事情不会第一反应想到找爸妈", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 993816}, {"id": 199950, "content": "遇到事情首先想到的不是向父母朋友寻求帮助 而是自己想办法解决", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1021563}, {"id": 200206, "content": "把自己照顾好，不让关心自己的人担心。\n经济独立，自己养活自己。\n为自己负责。", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 999099}, {"id": 201742, "content": "经济独立。并能帮助父母提高物质生活质量", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1001404}, {"id": 199951, "content": "不再想着父母会给你拿钱了 有任何困难会自己想办法解决~", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 981691}, {"id": 200207, "content": "独立", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 577887}, {"id": 200463, "content": "长大是自己委屈的眼泪都快出来了还能转身微笑着跟别人说话，像是什么事都没发生一样，然后还得忍着眼泪憋回去的难受劲儿", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1022994}, {"id": 211215, "content": "懂得独立，懂得珍惜，懂得放弃", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1017051}, {"id": 199952, "content": "时常无助，时常孤独", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 624627}, {"id": 200208, "content": "有自己的，不会轻易动摇的三观", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 627080}, {"id": 200720, "content": "爱上一匹野马，可我的家里没有草原。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1023677}]}